                <li>
Top 10 most desired traits for cybersecurity job candidates                </li>

    </ul>










            <header class="author-info">
                <div class="author">
                        <a href="https://www.scmagazine.com/doug-olenick/author/3633/" rel="author" title="Doug Olenick" class="author-avatar">
                            <img src="https://media.scmagazine.com/images/2016/11/07/blogdoug_1088714.jpg?format=jpg&amp;zoom=1&amp;quality=70&amp;anchor=middlecenter&amp;height=75&amp;width=135&amp;mode=crop" alt="Doug Olenick" title="Doug Olenick"  border="0"  />
                        </a>
                                            <div class="author-name">
                            <a href="https://www.scmagazine.com/doug-olenick/author/3633/" rel="author" title="Doug Olenick">by Doug Olenick, Online Editor</a>
                        </div>
                                            <div class="author-twitter"><a href='https://twitter.com/DougOlenick' class="twitter-follow-button" data-show-count="false" data-lang="en"></a>
