                            <h3>
                                <a onclick="addOmnitureEventForButtonClick(this, &#39;event71&#39;)" href="https://www.scmagazine.com/top-10-security-challenges-for-2017/article/682314/" title="" target="_self">
                                    Top 10 Security Challenges for 2017
                                </a>
                            </h3>                   
                            <div class="author-date">
    <span>BY
            <a rel="author" href="https://www.scmagazine.com/doug-olenick/author/3633/">Doug Olenick</a>

    </span>
                                 Aug 17, 2017
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <p class="image">
                                <a onclick="addOmnitureEventForButtonClick(this, &#39;event71&#39;)" href="https://www.scmagazine.com/top-10-ways-to-achieve-agile-security/article/644707/" title="" target="_self">
                                    <img src="https://media.scmagazine.com/images/2017/03/16/opinionsamilane_1181357.jpg?format=jpg&amp;zoom=1&amp;quality=70&amp;anchor=middlecenter&amp;height=120&amp;width=200&amp;mode=crop" alt="" title=""  border="0"  />
                                </a>
